        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 28 at 5:00PM PDT by NWS Pendleton OR</headline>
        <description>At 500 PM PDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Sisters, or 15 miles west of Redmond, moving north at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Sisters and Black Butte Ranch.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
